    </dl>
    
    <div class="Description">
      <h2>Description</h2>
      
      <p><code><a href='scale_area.html'>scale_area</a></code> is deprecated and will be
  removed in a future version of ggplot2. Use
  <code><a href='scale_size_area.html'>scale_size_area</a></code> instead. Note that the
  default behavir of <code><a href='scale_size_area.html'>scale_size_area</a></code> is
  slightly different: by default, it makes the area
  proportional to the numeric value.</p>
  
